oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mr. Burnett Job No. 38171
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); James, Sonny;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2731) for an order placed by Mr. Burnett for 2 orders of 100 two color window cards for a performance by Sonny James and others at the City Auditorium in Asheville, North Carolina on May 7. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
